						</div>

						<span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"branch\" id=\"branchPPI\">
						
					  		<p class=\"titleBarName1\">The following table summarizes the targets (from the tested set) that were used in this PPI network analysis. Background set is the source of the target frequency information for random network generation. For more detail, refer to the <b>Network Significance Test</b> below.</p>
					  		<table border=\"1\">
								<tr class=\"titleBarName1\">
									<th width=\"100\">
										&nbsp;
