							</table>
							
				            <p align=\"center\" class=\"sectionTitleName2\">Interaction Network Within Corpus (sorted by degree)</p>
				            <p class=\"titleBarName1\">[TABLE] Here is a summary table of the Protein-Protein Interaction network data of the test set. This table basically shows how many targets are interacting each other within the test set.</p>
                            <table border=\"1\" width=\"500\">
                                <tr class=\"titleBarName1\" onmouseover=\"Tip('<b>Num of PMIDs</b>: The number of papers from the test set (query).')\" onmouseout=\"UnTip()\">
